<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="attach-v">attach <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ə'tætʃ/    美 /ə'tætʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>系；贴；连接</strong></h4>
<p>to fasten or join one thing to another：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>attached</strong> a photo <strong>to</strong> my application form.
我在申请表上贴了一张照片。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>At the station, a board went up with dollar bills <strong>attached to</strong> it with pins.
车站竖起一个牌子，上面用别针别着些美元钞票。</p><footer>2019 浙江</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[正式用语] (与…) 有关联：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the advantage that <strong>attaches to</strong> wealth
与财富有关的有利条件</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>重视；认为...重要</strong></h4>
<p>to believe that sth is important or worth thinking about：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To be honest, a lot of people <strong>attach</strong> great <strong>importance to</strong> becoming rich and famous.  
坦白地说，很多人把名声和财富看得很重。</p><footer>人教② – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Learning strategies, <strong>to</strong> which teachers <strong>attach importance</strong> / <strong>significance</strong>, haven’t drawn enough attention of students.  
老师重视的学习策略还没有引起学生们足够的注意。</p><footer>2009 湖北改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>attached /ə'tætʃt/ adj <br />
1. ★ <strong>附着的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the attached application form
所附的申请表</p></div>

<ol>
<li>★ <strong>附属于：</strong>  </li>
</ol>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The research center <strong>is attached to</strong> the university.
这家研究中心附属于这所大学。</p></div>

<ol>
<li>★ <strong>喜欢的；依恋的：</strong>  </li>
</ol>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>At first, we didn’t feel we belong here, but now we <strong>are attached to</strong> the land we live on.
起初，我们感觉并不属于这里，但现在我们已经依恋上所生活的这片土地。</p><footer>北师大④ – 12</footer></div>

<p>attachment /ə'tætʃmənt/ n <br />
1. ★ <strong>[C] 附件；附属品：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please find my application letter and resume in the attachment.
请在附件中查看我的求职信和简历。</p><footer>2016 全国书面表达</footer></div>

<ol>
<li>★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 情感；爱慕：</strong>  </li>
</ol>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a child’s attachment to its mother
孩子对母亲的依恋</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>My parents always <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (对…很重视) my getting a good education.  （2014 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. attach great importance to  </p></div>